le just nearby the salt mine."},{"id":"marker6","name":"Stryt — silver mining town","legend":"Stryt is a mining town of 13094 people just nearby the silver mine."},{"id":"marker7","name":"Allantha Bridge","legend":"A formidable bridge spans over the Shroree River near Allantha."},{"id":"marker8","name":"Zakkaca Bridge","legend":"An old crossing of the Szazseika River, rarely used since the drying up of local trade."},{"id":"marker9","name":"The Dark Owl","legend":"A big and famous roadside tavern. Delicious marinated spinach with smoky rom is served here."},{"id":"marker10","name":"The Lucky Moose","legend":"A big and famous roadside inn. Delicious cured beans with shiny wine is served here."},{"id":"marker11","name":"The Golden Scorpion","legend":"A big and famous roadside inn. Delicious dressed scorpion with blue mead is served here."},{"id":"marker12","name":"The White Jackal","legend":"A big and famous roadside tavern. Delicious dried rat tails with bitter nectar is served here."},{"id":"marker13","name":"The Hungry Tavern","legend":"A big and famous roadside tavern. Delicious baked pigeon with dark sap is served here."},{"id":"marker14","name":"The Big Scorpion","legend":"A big and famous roadside tavern. Delicious corned cake with golden vodka is served here."},{"id":"marker15","name":"Cielb Waterfall","legend":"A gorgeous waterfall flows here."},{"id":"marker16","name":"Rhiq Battlefield","legend":"A historical battle of the Qhosh Invasion. \r\nDate: January 2, 1555 Betheso Era."},{"id":"marker17","name":"Liavud Battlefield","legend":"A historical battle of the Racan Conflict. \r\nDate: September 2, 1525 Betheso Era."},{"id":"marker18","name":"Dungeon","legend":"<div>Undiscovered dungeon. See <a href=\"https://watabou.github.io/one-page-dungeon/?seed=61064363275\" target=\"_blank\">One page dungeon</a></div><iframe style=\"pointer-events: none;\" src=\"https://watabou.github.io/one-page-dungeon/?seed=61064363275\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin\"></iframe>"},{"id":"marker19","name":"Dungeon","legend":"<div>Undiscovered dungeon. See <a href=\"https://watabou.github.io/one-page-dungeon/?seed=610643698\" target=\"_blank\">One page dungeon</a></div><iframe style=\"pointer-events: none;\" src=\"https://watabou.github.io/one-page-dungeon/?seed=610643698\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin\"></iframe>"},{"id":"marker20","name":"Saica Monster","legend":"Locals say a relic monster of 9 m long inhabits Saica Lake. Truth or lie, folks are afraid to fish in the lake."},{"id":"marker21","name":"Botford Monster","legend":"Old sailors tell stories of a gigantic sea monster inhabiting these dangerous waters. Rumors say it can be 23 m long."},{"id":"marker22","name":"Alonarauthyl Bearded Devil","legend":"Rumors speak of a terrifying Bearded Devil who inhabits Alonarauthyl hills and steals cattle at night."},{"id":"marker23","name":"Zach Forest","legend":"A forest sacred to local Arago (Arachnid) Deities."},{"id":"marker24","name":"Marazandostamn Pinery","legend":"A pinery sacred to local Rake (Drakonic) Gods."},{"id":"marker25","name":"Rheerhod Hawks","legend":"A gang of forest brigands."},{"id":"marker26","name":"Sas'suria Dogs","legend":"A gang of forest brigands."},{"id":"marker27","name":"Qavhieli Ravens","legend":"A gang of forest brigands."},{"id":"marker28","name":"Vigbiruru Jaguars","legend":"A gang of forest bandits."},{"id":"marker29","name":"Pirates","legend":"Pirate ships have been spotted in these waters."},{"id":"marker30","name":"Pirates","legend":"Pirate ships have been spotted in these waters."},{"id":"marker31","name":"Pirates","legend":"Pirate ships have been spotted in these waters."},{"id":"marker32","name":"Krudhnud Stele","legend":"An ancient stele. It has an inscription, but no one can translate it:\n        <div style=\"font-size: 1.8em; line-break: anywhere;\">ሀከፐሰዐ የኀቀሠ ደ ጠ ረ ፈዘጸኀሐበፈወጸጰገሠተወነደፈሰበጰተገ  ፐገጸነረፈጰኀ ኀነዐገገሀዘሐነፈሠዐፀሰወበጠተበሠፀመረየሀአዘበ ዐዘሀፐገወ ሠዘጸሰነፈሀከ</div>"},{"id":"marker33","name":"Rever Effigy","legend":"An ancient effigy. It has an inscription, but no one can translate it:\n        <div style=\"font-size: 1.8em; line-break: anywhere;\">𐠦\udc2f  𐠴𐠛\udc27\ud802\ud802\ud802\ud802\ud802 \udc13\ud802𐠩\ud802𐠗\udc19𐠗\ud802𐠥\ud802\ud802\ud802𐠡\ud802𐠥𐠧\udc32\ud802\ud802𐠡\ud802\ud802𐠰\udc0d𐠑\udc37\udc0c\udc1b𐠪𐠊</div>"},{"id":"marker34","name":"Kharakkek Effigy","legend":"An ancient effigy. It has an inscription, but no one can translate it:\n        <div style=\"font-size: 1.8em; line-break: anywhere;\">\udc3c\ud802𐠜\udc2e𐠧\udc08\udc28\udc1a\udc03𐠮\udc34\udc3c\udc22𐠧\udc24𐠅\udc2e\udc0d𐠸\ud802\ud802𐠱\udc2b\udc13\ud802𐠸 \udc21𐠛𐠄\udc08\ud802 \ud802 𐠚\udc15\udc15\ud802𐠮\udc0c\udc18𐠧</div>"},{"id":"marker35","name":"Ruined Pyramid","legend":"Ruins of an ancient pyramid. Untold riches may lie within."},{"id":"marker36","name":"Ruined Town","legend":"Ruins of an ancient town. Untold riches may lie within."},{"id":"marker37","name":"Ruined Settlement","legend":"Ruins of an ancient settlement. Untold riches may lie within."},{"id":"marker38","name":"Srach Library","legend":"A vast collection of knowledge, including many rare and ancient tomes."},{"id":"marker39","name":"Travelling Extraordinary Circus","legend":"Roll up, roll up, this extraordinary circus is here for a limited time only."},{"id":"marker40","name":"Travelling Incomprehensible Circus","legend":"Roll up, roll up, this incomprehensible circus is here for a limited time only."},{"id":"marker41","name":"Rhevied Contest","legend":"Warriors from around the land gather for a contest of might in Rhevied, with fame, fortune and favour on offer to the victor."},{"id":"marker42","name":"Omindrikalgen Fair","legend":"A fair is being held in Omindrikalgen, with all manner of local and foreign goods and services on offer."},{"id":"marker43","name":"Minor Jetty","legend":"A small location along the Gazd River to launch boats from sits here, along with a weary looking owner, willing to sell passage along the river."},{"id":"marker44","name":"Ibises migration","legend":"A huge group of ibises are migrating, whether part of their annual routine, or something more extraordinary."},{"id":"marker45","name":"Fenptangalag Cave","legend":"The Fenptangalag Cave. Locals claim that it is slowly filling with lava."},{"id":"marker46","name":"Rhai Portal","legend":"An element of the magic portal system connecting major cities. The portals were installed centuries ago, but still work fine."},{"id":"marker47","name":"Eziel Portal","legend":"An element of the magic portal system connecting major cities. The portals were installed centuries ago, but still work fine."},{"id":"marker48","name":"Lhi Portal","legend":"An element of the magic portal system connecting major cities. The portals were installed centuries ago, but still work fine."},{"id":"marker49","name":"Rhir'ih Portal","legend":"An element of the magic portal system connecting major cities. The portals were installed centuries ago, but still work fine."},{"id":"marker50","name":"Gosharb Portal","legend":"An element of the magic portal system connecting major cities. The portals were installed centuries ago, but still work fine."},{"id":"marker51","name":"Interdimensional Rift","legend":"A rumoured interdimensional rift in this area is causing nearby plants to wither and decay."},{"id":"marker52","name":"Disturbed Burial","legend":"A burial site has been disturbed in this area, causing the dead to rise and attack the living."},{"id":"marker53","name":"Disturbed Burial","legend":"A burial site has been disturbed in this area, causing the dead to rise and attack the living."},{"id":"marker54","name":"Thres Mausoleum","legend":"Rising from the desolate landscape, this sinister necropolis is a testament to necromantic power. Its skeletal spires cast ominous shadows, concealing forbidden knowledge and arcane secrets."},{"id":"marker55","name":"Random encounter","legend":"<div>You have encountered a character.</div><iframe src=\"https://deorum.vercel.app/encounter/1497\" width=\"375\" height=\"600\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups\"></iframe>"},{"id":"marker56","name":"Random encounter","legend":"<div>You have encountered a character.</div><iframe src=\"https://deorum.vercel.app/encounter/1692\" width=\"375\" height=\"600\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups\"></iframe>"},{"id":"marker57","name":"Random encounter","legend":"<div>You have encountered a character.</div><iframe src=\"https://deorum.vercel.app/encounter/3907\" width=\"375\" height=\"600\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups\"></iframe>"},{"id":"marker58","name":"Random encounter","legend":"<div>You have encountered a character.</div><iframe src=\"https://deorum.vercel.app/encounter/3184\" width=\"375\" height=\"600\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups\"></iframe>"},{"id":"marker59","name":"Random encounter","legend":"<div>You have encountered a character.</div><iframe src=\"https://deorum.vercel.app/encounter/1959\" width=\"375\" height=\"600\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups\"></iframe>"},{"id":"marker60","name":"Random encounter","legend":"<div>You have encountered a character.</div><iframe src=\"https://deorum.vercel.app/encounter/1354\" width=\"375\" height=\"600\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups\"></iframe>"}]
